Website: check out @user5. It looks easy, it renders very well, and it's Open Source. I will migrate one of my sites to it before the next renewal.
Signal: check out cal.com. It's an Open Source scheduling service, with integrations to schedule video calls with Element, JITSI, etc. They also support Signal, but I haven't tested whether it's for messages or video.
I recommend @user6. End-to-end encryption, decentralized, Open Source.
